/**
 * \page load_module Use Chan_SCCP
 * \section cs_load_module_howto How to load the Chan_SCCP
 *
 * The chan_sccp module can be loaded using the following lines in asterisk module.conf:
 *
 * load => chan_sccp.conf
 *
 * noload => chan_skinn.so
 *
 * the skinny module is not allowed to be loaded, is it conflicts with chan_sccp.
 * 
 * \section necessities Necessities
 * A valid sccp.conf/sccp_v3.conf configfile has to be available in the asterisk configuration directory.
 *
 **/

